There are limited data concerning the use of biosimilars of filgrastim in autologous stem cell transplantation (ASCT).

 This study aimed to evaluate G-CSF efficiency and safety (based on haemograms, transfusion needs and complications) of two biosimilars (Zarzio and Ratiograstim(R)) compared to those of Neupogen(R) for our patients who underwent ASCT.

